<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <p xml:id="Aink225-kilavi">melivu kūṟi varaivukaṭāvak kēṭṭa talaimakaṉ tāṉ varaitaṟ poruṭṭāl oruvaḻittaṇantu nīṭṭittāṉāka vāṟṟāḷākiya talaimakaṭkut tōḻi kūṟiyatu. </p>
      <p xml:lang="en">What the confidante told the heroine, who had become unable to endure it, as the hero—who had listened as [she] urged him to marry [the heroine], speaking of her weakness—delayed [his arrival/the marriage] having become ‘temporarily-absent-from-her-place’ for the purpose of marrying [her]. </p>
    </div>
  <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink225">
<l>amma vāḻi tōḻi paiñcuṉaip</l>
<l>pācaṭai nivanta paṉimalark kuvaḷai</l>
<l>yuḷḷakaṅ kamaḻuṅ kūntaṉ melliya</l>
<l>lōti yoṇṇutal pacatta</l>
<l>lōrār koṉṉaṅ kāta lōrē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
        <l>  Alas, O friend! </l>
        <l>Our lover does not care </l>
        <l rend="space indent">for the paling of the bright forehead [of you who are] delicate in nature, </l>
        <l rend="indent2">[whose] tresses are inwardly fragrant with blue water-lilies,  </l>
        <l rend="indent3">[their] dewy blossoms rising from green leaves in the fresh mountain spring.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
